{"tid":1605792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 原來十一 各大巴士公司會有行動","createTime":"2019-09-30T11:40:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T12:11:46.000Z","uid":248907,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a9afd8802897f011d0632c30cecaed306667239b","tid":1605792,"uid":248907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:40:18.000Z","msg":"其實係想手足一齊推下黑箱車行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n時間係朝早去賀壽個陣<br />\n地點各大小巴士線<br />\n<br />\n大家自備賀佢老母文宣（例如白花、白布條、黑白文宣等等)，上巴士之後貼係玻璃窗，車頭就梗係痴相<br />\n<br />\n賀完壽入黑，希望大家盡翻公民責任，清理上午借用嘅巴士車箱，帶走貼左嘅文宣同物件，就算唔係同一架巴士，都可以幫手清理<br />\n<br />\n最緊要記得用皺紋膠紙/blue tack等不留痕跡嘅黏貼用品，落車講翻聲唔該司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一齊 十。一 賀佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"031284087b80a1e5de4ec6dc3eff33ae2af735c8","tid":1605792,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:44:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8fdfc1a83cd0b4e03ef0b39fe1d7684c75c65d68","tid":1605792,"uid":42534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:59:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3975d3536cd4caf201676fbfb8878461bc55eba7","tid":1605792,"uid":100299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:02:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"31ab754abc5de634f939760a9c1b4644ef5206dc","tid":1605792,"uid":42235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:03:07.000Z","msg":"呢個方法幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e5455c6a63ab7cd3e1e6b6dab3266f2a2f12fff","tid":1605792,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:05:37.000Z","msg":"流動連農墻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"038424eab835725b65fef0d52c2c5c3a027eea95","tid":1605792,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0